    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to show you this car\u2014it\u2019s an absolute gem and looks just as good as the day it rolled off the lot! It has been pampered like a member of the family, kept tucked away in the garage, and it still runs like an absolute dream. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here; it\u2019s basically in showroom condition and ready for its next adventure. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself! You\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
