    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L powerplant and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full double-VANOS rebuild and rod bearing replacement using upgraded shells. The rear subframe\u2014a known structural weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced to exceed factory specifications. Performance is razor-sharp thanks to the Variable M Differential Lock and a chassis that retains its original torsional rigidity. The exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or trim delamination. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who values engineering integrity and peak S54 performance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
