    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a deep, mirror-like gloss with zero imperfections\u2014absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks\u2014thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and consistent climate-controlled storage. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, the dash is free of any UV damage, and the interior still retains that fresh factory scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history exclusively from the original dealership, including a recent comprehensive inspection and fluid flush. The matching set of high-performance tires has less than 500 miles on them, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body panels. This vehicle has never seen rain, has never been smoked in, and has been meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner. Complete with all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a pristine vehicle history report.",
